com.danielly.jsf.cinema.services

Class SearchSelectionList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.danielly.jsf.cinema.services.SearchSelectionList

  • @Named(value="search_data")
 @RequestScoped
public class SearchSelectionList
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class SearchSelectionList is used in the search component. It presents the selection to the user to search from the existing showtimes. In addition, return the filter showtimes after the search.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Gil Danielly
